{"tid":1980460,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[八達通收費㗎...] 水務署銅鑼灣賣水站遭撬鐵閘毀夾萬 賊人空手而回","createTime":"2020-04-20T06:07:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T17:29:00.000Z","uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6d61167cb50281fa7ee89248612aa83f735477dc","tid":1980460,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:07:50.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣維園道食水賣水站，今晨(20日)約8時，警方接獲上址水務署職員報案，指賣水站的鐵門鎖被撬開，懷疑被人爆竊，於是報警。警方到場了解，初步發現賣水站一個夾萬被毀爛，正調查賊人去向。<br />\n據悉，涉事賣水站位於上址海旁，由水務署運作用以售賣淡水予附近船舶使用。水務署發言人指，經點算後證實站內並無現金或其他損失。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200420/photo/bkn-20200420090916484-0420_00822_001_01b.jpg?20200420135512\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200420%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200420090916484-0420_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20200420135512&h=3d9a6853&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e105a42447e988cf857e4dd15e69d4fa67a673c6","tid":1980460,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:09:03.000Z","msg":"水務署現有7個食水售賣站，分別位於港九新界的海傍位置，以供船舶使用，如顧客需取用食水，可於售賣站以八達通購買，或到水務署列明的地點購買水票。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200420/_2020042010012955143.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200420%2F_2020042010012955143.jpg&h=efafb34c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿公岩食水售賣站<br />\n香港筲箕灣避風塘(譚公廟道海傍) <br />\n銅鑼灣食水售賣站<br />\n香港銅鑼灣避風塘(維園道海傍) <br />\n西灣河食水售賣站<br />\n香港筲箕灣太康街(西灣河海濱公園海傍) <br />\n西區食水售賣站<br />\n香港上環西消防街(近中山紀念公園海傍) <br />\n油麻地食水售賣站<br />\n九龍油麻地避風塘(海輝道海傍) <br />\n屯門食水售賣站<br />\n新界屯門蝴蝶灣湖翠路(近慧豐園海傍) <br />\n荔枝角食水售賣站<br />\n九龍荔枝角興華街西(船廠側海傍)"},{"pid":"76e88d9c72e6013667e7c66ea6d22981b4100d4b","tid":1980460,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:09:19.000Z","msg":"購買水票：<br />\n<br />\n九龍區<br />\n大角咀客戶諮詢中心<br />\n<br />\n大角咀客戶諮詢中心不設收費服務，客戶可攜繳費單到任何郵政局以現金或支票繳費，或到任何7-Eleven便利店、OK便利店、VanGO便利店或香港華潤萬家超級市場以現金繳費（每次繳費金額上限為港幣5,000元）。<br />\n<br />\n水票售賣時間為星期一至五由上午九時十五分至下午五時正。星期六、日及公眾假期休息。另外，客戶亦可到筲箕灣譚公廟道10號筲箕灣海事分處購買水票。"},{"pid":"e1124812c41cbd7fa0c7e3f38039ffda8020341b","tid":1980460,"uid":315329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:10:19.000Z","msg":"八達通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad2e8102797fafe408b9d9c9181c400f3a500122","tid":1980460,"uid":7439,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e1124812c41cbd7fa0c7e3f38039ffda8020341b","tid":1980460,"uid":315329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:10:19.000Z","msg":"八達通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:37:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9FB57c3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9FB57c3.gif&h=45627e9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee367b21ae1ade168ce771ea35db9c337d8d3404","tid":1980460,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad2e8102797fafe408b9d9c9181c400f3a500122","tid":1980460,"uid":7439,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e1124812c41cbd7fa0c7e3f38039ffda8020341b","tid":1980460,"uid":315329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:10:19.000Z","msg":"八達通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"